.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, horror, scientific, romance
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
5 different games are played: snooker, whist, go, canasta, billiard
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
City: liverpool, prague, hamburg, edinburgh, new-york

1. the english is the person watching epic movies
2. the spanish is the person traveling to liverpool
3. the person drinking coffee is the person watching martial-arts movies
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is to the right of the person watching horror movies
6. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to new-york
7. the person playing whist is the person watching scientific movies
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague
11. the person playing whist is to the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh
12. the person playing canasta is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the person playing billiard
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person watching romance movies

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Movie-Genre		|    scientific	|      romance	|      epic	|     horror	|     martial-arts	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Game		|     whist	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| canasta	|   parliament	|
| City		|     prague	|     edinburgh	|     new-york	|     liverpool	|     hamburg	|
